  "body": "This ticket is a follow up of [update community home screens](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/14018#top)\r\n#14018\r\n\r\n### ISSUE 1 Scrolling on initial community screen doesn't work\r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n\r\n1. Add a lot of communities (more that list can display)\r\n2. Try to scroll through the list\r\n3. Observe the result\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** scrolling doesn't work\r\n\r\n**Expected result:** scrolling works\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/198568030-309fcd79-91d6-42ca-8858-5728d044aa74.mp4\r\n\r\n### ISSUE 2 Empty community screen misses some elements that Figma design has: icons at Discover card, text and image in the empty list\r\n\r\n**Actual:**\r\n![photo_2022-10-28 13 44 41](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/198569539-7027ae40-553a-4e5d-b55b-9d050f9f4ac5.jpeg)\r\n\r\n**Expected:** \r\n\r\n![Communities for Mobile – Figma 2022-10-28 13-43-52](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/198569574-d0080e3e-783a-4b2b-9923-d7e276bd6a23.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### ISSUE 3 Missing accessability ids for some elements\r\n\r\n1. Discover card\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1242\" alt=\"Appium 2022-10-28 14-09-19\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/198573706-d5bef1db-b6c7-452f-87a0-10857282df8f.png\">\r\n\r\n2. Filter buttons (Joined, Pending, Opened) \r\n\r\n<img width=\"427\" alt=\"Appium 2022-10-28 14-10-55\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/198573895-9b51cabc-71b0-4933-bb11-c74d24e6dce9.png\">\r\n\r\n3. Discover Communities scrollbar with categories elements\r\n\r\n<img width=\"420\" alt=\"Appium 2022-10-28 16-27-15\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/198610348-3e1cc0a2-2d39-4fd0-9d20-5c424af9e16e.png\">\r\n\r\n4. Filter tabs, Sort and View buttons on Discover Communities screen\r\n\r\n<img width=\"423\" alt=\"Appium 2022-10-28 16-29-49\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/198612465-02896813-f249-4dc7-8987-864b59498a7f.png\">\r\n\r\n5. Sort Communities options elements\r\n\r\n<img width=\"427\" alt=\"Appium 2022-10-28 16-37-28\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/198616637-b487c507-07b9-48f7-84c1-e83cbac77600.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### ISSUE 4 White screen splashes when redirecting to Discover communities screen (might be some global problem, not PR related)\r\n\r\nI am reproducing an ISSUE with 4+ communities added to the list. Better to reproduce with the dark mode on. \r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n\r\n1. Add 4+ communities \r\n2. Open Discover communities screen\r\n3. Pay attention at white screen that flashes during redirection\r\n\r\n**Actual result:**\r\nWhite screen splashes when redirecting to Discover communities screen\r\n\r\n**Expected result:** no white screen splash\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/198599715-71bc9c0b-a970-4067-be5d-2e987dc4a582.mp4\r\n\r\n### ISSUE 5 Sort Communities options are missing icons\r\n\r\n**Actual:**\r\n\r\n![photo_2022-10-28 16 20 09](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/198605537-147c3ea7-3c29-4282-8798-f3d4cb0c5e9e.jpeg)\r\n\r\n**Figma:**\r\n\r\n![Communities for Mobile – Figma 2022-10-28 16-21-44](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/198606618-7fbc8280-bae9-44f4-94f4-1071eff9eeaa.png)\r\n\r\n### ISSUE 6 Expand categories is missing on Discover communities screen\r\n\r\n**Figma:** \r\n\r\n![Communities for Mobile – Figma 2022-10-28 16-41-47](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/198620002-bd26526b-eab0-4a91-bfc6-e386ddb00c3d.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
